strings.Value: "I'm so tired, just dead on my feet."
"I didn't know you could ever get tired. This is a rare sight indeed!"
"You are stronger than most. Others would fall long before you."
"I know you won't heed my advice, Amiri. But you really must take care of yourself. Everyone has limits."

[Writing in her notebook, and mumbling to herself] "This longsome journey depleted my strength — it's time to lay our heads! The beasts of the night shall not disturb your peace, my friends! said the tireless warrior..."
You exert yourself carelessly, without thinking of tomorrow... You are like a candle lit on both ends. – You shine brightly, but you burn quickly!"
